<HEADLINE> Ministry: 400,000 Russians Take Part in May Day Events </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, May 1 (Xinhua) -- The Russian Interior Ministry said
Monday that 412,800 people took part in various May Day events in
84 of the 89 regions across the country, the Interfax news agency
reported.
</P>
<P>
About 70,000 police and 4,376 Interior Ministry troops had been
on duty nationwide, but there were no reports of any violence, the
ministry press center said.
</P>
<P>
