<HEADLINE> hke050134-- Int'l Labor Day Observed in Indonesia </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JAKARTA, May 1 (Xinhua) -- The International Labor Day was
observed here Monday with thousands workers from various labor
organizations in the country staging a demonstration at the
legislative assembly building.
</P>
<P>
