scored 12 minutes into the match, lofting a 10-meter header past
goalkeeper Noel Valladares.
</P>
<P>
Suazo, who plays for Cagiliari in Italy, came up with the
equaliser in the 29th minute, powering in a 12-meter shot off a
pass by his cousin Maynor Suazo.
</P>
<P>
