<HEADLINE> Income Index of Major Chinese Regions: Beijing </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, May 1 (Xinhua) -- The following is the latest income
situation for urban dwellers in Beijing, the Chinese capital, in
the first quarter of the year:
</P>
<P>
The average per capita disposable income of urban dwellers in
Beijing reached 2,708.6 yuan in the quarter, a year-on-year
increase of 15 percent. But the actual income increase climbed
only 13.4 percent after taking price changes into account.
</P>
